  "html": "\n<div><center>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><font><img src=\"../images/R.gif\"/> </font><b>swallow\n        swallow ...</b><hr noshade=\"\"/>\n<p>Cf. Swinburne's \"Itylus\", which begins,\n        \"Swallow, my sister, O sister swallow, / How can\n        thine heart be full of spring?\" and Tennyson's lyric\n        in <em>The Princess </em>\"O Swallow, Swallow,\n        flying, flying south.\"</p>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td> </td>\n<td><a href=\"title_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Waste_A.htm\"><font>back to \"The Waste Land\" </font></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</center></div>\n",
